These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, turkish
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | turkish |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, country
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
2 different games are played: bridge, poker
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Game       | poker  | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | june  | july |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
City: berlin, rome
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| City   | rome        | berlin  |

